title: february 1: d is for dictionary
description:
Today on 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the beginning of one of the most complex dictionaries: the Oxford English Dictionary. Afterwards, she discusses how a certain type of record made the jukebox possible. Join this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
